commit.message:
setuptools_wrap: Fix unknown setup options related to cmake_process_manifest_hook keyword

This commit addresses a regression introduced in 66d7a32  (Add hook to process
cmake install manifest) and prevents setuptools from complaining about unknown
setup options.

It removes cmake_process_manifest_hook keyword from argument dict.
